Quickstrike:







Quickstrike felt woozy from something. He ducked his head, being beside 
Megatron and Rattrap. He remembered being cornered, and felt something 
scratch across his chest seconds before Rattrap pulled his butt out of the 
fire. He bobbed his head, feeling weak. His leg felt terrible.
He looked down as he saw a open wound on it, exposing some metal work. He 
moaned, keeping his head down.
